{"tid":1243545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港示威者淋熄催淚彈「揚威海外」，外媒讚簡單有，阻催淚粉末氣化！","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:49:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15e4a1b6ebdd727be7a455db421fe3f8914561d4","tid":1243545,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"上周三（6 月12日）發生的警民衝突中，警方發射 150 枚催淚彈、布袋彈和橡膠子彈等，現場示威者迅速地把警方發射的催淚彈以水淋熄，片段在互聯網上「瘋傳」，有外媒甚至認為，這個減低催淚彈殺傷力的「香港方法」，可能成為未來抵抗警察暴力的另類方法。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2FD980C2-EB8D-42A9-9CCA-D74D86F599D92028129_bOLg7_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2FD980C2-EB8D-42A9-9CCA-D74D86F599D92028129_bOLg7_1200x0.jpeg&h=e4fde6b6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n美國知名時事政評雜誌《Slate》指，稱讚香港示威者，面對暴力時展現超卓的組織力及韌力。在網上瘋傳的片段中，示威者迅速圍著警方發射、冒煙的催淚彈，並以水淋熄，再用交通「雪糕筒」和安全帽等遮蓋，再把催淚彈拋走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。外國網民對示威者行動表達讚賞和充滿好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，問道：「真的這樣簡單就可以化解淚彈的殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？」<br />\n<br />\n美國北卡羅來納州杜克大學麻醉學副教授 Sven Eric Jordt 在訪問中指，催淚彈殺傷力的核心，來自彈中的白色粉末，當催淚彈發射後，透過加熱化學粉末變成催淚氣體，令人咳嗽、大量流淚。<br />\n<br />\n他說，如果像片中示威者般以水淋熄催淚彈的話，彈中的粉末就不能氣化，而水更可以令粉末中的催淚化學成份不再活躍，這也是為何中了催淚彈後，淋水就可以紓緩皮膚刺痛的感覺。<br />\n<br />\nJordt 指，很少看到這樣有組織地淋熄催淚彈的行動，可能是因為[香港示威者組織得特別好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過這樣做，很可能會引來警方進一步以武力針對。<br />\n<br />\n2013 年土耳其反政府抗議運動中，有示威者把射出的大型催淚彈，放入水桶中然後密封，行動十分成功，不過或會有爆炸風險。不過，由於片中的催淚彈較小，故此數樽清水也能應付，警方很可能備有更大型的催淚彈，屆時就不是幾樽水能應付到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-佔領-港示威者淋熄催淚彈-揚威海外-外媒讚簡單有效-阻催淚粉末氣化/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E7%86%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E8%AE%9A%E7%B0%A1%E5%96%AE%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E9%98%BB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AB%E6%B0%A3%E5%8C%96%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu77zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=daad981f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%8B%E7%86%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E8%AE%9A%E7%B0%A1%E5%96%AE%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E9%98%BB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AB%E6%B0%A3%E5%8C%96%2F&h=6410a509\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-佔領-港示威者淋熄催淚彈-揚威海外-外媒讚簡單有效-阻催淚粉末氣化/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2019/06/hong-kong-tear-gas-water-bottle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Fnews-and-politics%2F2019%2F06%2Fhong-kong-tear-gas-water-bottle.html&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu77zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=e65d26fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2019/06/hong-kong-tear-gas-water-bottle.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://9gag.com/gag/aD1vzpZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F9gag.com%2Fgag%2FaD1vzpZ&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu77zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=0df347e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://9gag.com/gag/aD1vzpZ</a>"},{"pid":"a8ac6bd1bc22cde82ed10715aac4c76edd9b9abc","tid":1243545,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題：香港示威者淋熄催淚彈「揚威海外」，外媒讚簡單有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">效</span></strong>，阻催淚粉末氣化！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"09f80ec9f1aca165406edb2aa7d49004d630c6ea","tid":1243545,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"其實你地淋熄催淚彈係無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1216115\" target=\"_blank\">https://li